add_ons.description: A JSON string with the results of the Add-ons you specified in the `add_ons` parameters. For the format of the object, see [Using Add-ons](https://www.twilio.com/docs/add-ons).

caller_name.description: The name of the phone number's owner. If `null`, that information was not available.

carrier.description: The telecom company that provides the phone number.

country_code.description: The [ISO country code](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_3166-1_alpha-2) for the phone number.

national_format.description: The phone number, in national format.

phone_number.description: The phone number in [E.164](https://www.twilio.com/docs/glossary/what-e164) format, which consists of a + followed by the country code and subscriber number.

url.description: The absolute URL of the resource.
